#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.65"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.65:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.65:0.2"
msgid "7. Yamakavagga "
msgstr "7. Pairs "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.65:0.3"
msgid "65. Paṭhamasukhasutta "
msgstr "65. Happiness (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.121, sc1
msgctxt "an10.65:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto magadhesu viharati nālakagāmake. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying in the land of the Magadhans near the little village of Nālaka. "

msgctxt "an10.65:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sāmaṇḍakāni paribbājako yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the wanderer Sāmaṇḍakāni went up to Venerable Sāriputta and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an10.65:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho sāmaṇḍakāni paribbājako āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Sāmaṇḍakāni sat down to one side, and said to Sāriputta: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.65:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, sukhaṃ, kiṃ dukkhan”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, what is happiness and what is suffering?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.65:2.2"
msgid "“Abhinibbatti kho, āvuso, dukkhā, anabhinibbatti sukhā. "
msgstr "“Rebirth is suffering, reverend, no rebirth is happiness. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.3"
msgid "Abhinibbattiyā, āvuso, sati idaṃ dukkhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr "When there is rebirth, you can expect this kind of suffering. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.4"
msgid "sītaṃ uṇhaṃ jighacchā pipāsā uccāro passāvo aggisamphasso daṇḍasamphasso satthasamphasso ñātīpi mittāpi saṅgamma samāgamma rosenti. "
msgstr "Cold, heat, hunger, thirst, defecation, and urination. Contact with fire, clubs, and knives. And relatives and friends get together and annoy you. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.5"
msgid "Abhinibbattiyā, āvuso, sati idaṃ dukkhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is rebirth, this is the kind of suffering you can expect. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.6"
msgid "Anabhinibbattiyā, āvuso, sati idaṃ sukhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr "When there is no rebirth, you can expect this kind of happiness. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.7"
msgid "na sītaṃ na uṇhaṃ na jighacchā na pipāsā na uccāro na passāvo na aggisamphasso na daṇḍasamphasso na satthasamphasso ñātīpi mittāpi saṅgamma samāgamma na rosenti. "
msgstr "No cold, heat, hunger, thirst, defecation, or urination. No contact with fire, clubs, or knives. And relatives and friends don’t get together and annoy you. "

msgctxt "an10.65:2.8"
msgid "Anabhinibbattiyā, āvuso, sati idaṃ sukhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhan”ti. "
msgstr "When there is no rebirth, this is the kind of happiness you can expect.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.65:2.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
